Choose Sprint as your cell phone carrier and discover how the best value in wireless keeps you connected to the things that matter most to you. Find the latest cell phones available with blazing-fast 4G LTE speeds and choose unlimited data or opt for Sprint's new Family Share Pack with plenty of data to go around. Find online deals for both new and certified pre-owned cell phones including the newest iPhone 6, or stop by a Sprint retail store and let our experts help you find the perfect cell phone and plan for you.
**Monthly charges exclude taxes & Sprint Surcharges [incl. USF charge of up to 17.40% (varies quarterly), up to $2.50 Admin. & .40 Reg. /line/mo.) & fees by area (approx. 5-20%)]. Surcharges are not taxes. See .. 